Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html#/s:8Curr.name: name
Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html#/s:8Curr.abstract: The name of the currency, such as “United States Dollar”.

Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html#/s:8Curr.name: minorUnits
Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html#/s:8Curr.abstract: The number of decimal digits used to express minor units of the currency.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: minorUnits
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: The amount represented as a whole number of the currency’s “minorUnits”.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: amount
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: The bankers rounded amount of money being represented, as defined by the currency.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: init(minorUnits:)
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: Creates a representation of the provided amount as the currency’s exact smallest unit.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: init(amount:)
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: Creates a representation of the provided amount in the desired currency, if it can be represented.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: distributedEvenly(intoParts:)
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: Distributes the current amount into a set number of parts as evenly as possible.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: distributedProportionally(between:)
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: Distributes the current amount between other amounts proportionally based on their original value.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.name: negated()
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html#/s:8Currency0.abstract: Returns the current value as its additive inverse.

Protocols/AnyCurrency.html.name: AnyCurrency
Protocols/AnyCurrency.html.abstract: A representation of a value in a specific currency that can be used as an existential.

Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html.name: CurrencyMetadata
Protocols/CurrencyMetadata.html.abstract: A type that provides static currency information as defined by ISO 4217.

Protocols/CurrencyProtocol.html.name: CurrencyProtocol
Protocols/CurrencyProtocol.html.abstract: A representation of a value in a specific currency.

Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.name: sum()
Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.abstract: Returns the sum total of all amounts in the sequence.

Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.name: sum(where:)
Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.abstract: Returns the sum total of all amounts in the sequence that satify the given predicate.

Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.name: sum(_:)
Extensions/Sequence.html#/s:ST8CurrencyA.abstract: Returns the sum total of amounts in the sequence after applying the provided transform.

Classes/CurrencyMint/CurrencyIdentifier..name: init(_:)
Classes/CurrencyMint/CurrencyIdentifier..abstract: Creates an identifier to represent the alphabetic code.

Classes/CurrencyMint/CurrencyIdentifier..name: init(_:)
Classes/CurrencyMint/CurrencyIdentifier..abstract: Creates an identifier to represent the numeric code.

Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.name: IdentifierLookup
Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.abstract: A closure that receives a currency identifier and finds a matching concrete currency type.

Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.name: standard
Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.abstract: Returns a shared currency generator that only provides ISO 4217 defined currencies.

Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.name: init(fallbackLookup:)
Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.abstract: Creates an instance that will use the provided lookup closure if an identifier doesn’t match the ISO 4217 specification.

Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.name: init(defaultCurrency:)
Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.abstract: Creates an instance that will always resolves the provided currency type when ISO 4217 specification lookup fails.

Classes/CurrencyMint.html#/s:8Currency0A.name: make(identifier:minorUnits:)
